# Code Style & Quality

## Naming & Formatting
- Variables/functions: `snake_case`
- Classes: `PascalCase`  
- 4 spaces, 88 char limit (Black formatting)
- Type hints required on all functions

## Quality Standards
- No wildcard imports or mutable defaults
- Prefer early returns over nested conditionals
- Use Flake8, Pylint, Mypy for static analysis
- Google-style docstrings for public APIs